Package dxf2svg

Class Summary
Dxf2Svg This is the entry point into the application.
Dxf2SvgLogger This class can be invoked to output errors or any information you wish.
DxfConverter This class actually coordinates the building of the SVG graphic.
DxfPreprocessor The DxfPreprocessor instantiates and controls the multithreaded conversion environment of the DxfConverter.
FigureSheetDatabase This class is a trivial wrapper for the dxf2svg.util.Database class.
HtmlWrapperBuilder This class performs the complex activity of generating the HTML wrapper files.
LibCatUtil This class is intended as a utility to manage LibraryCatalog.ser files.
LibraryCatalog This class is a wrapper class to implement namespaces for FigureSheetDatabases (see DatabaseContainer for more details.
StyleSheetGenerator This class will generate internal or external style sheets for SVG depending on the stylesheet option switch on the command line.
SvgBuilder This is where all the SVG objects output their results to the final SVG file.
SvgNoteManager This class creates and manages all of the SvgNotes that will be required during the current conversion process.
SvgUnZip This class is a quick little file unzipper for svgz files.
SvgZip This class is a quick little SVG zipper.
 

Exception Summary
NullDxfConverterReferenceException This unchecked exception signals that the client application attempted to pass a null DxfConverter object reference.
